                  </table-column>
               </table-row>
               
               
               
               
               
               
               
               
            </table></section-body></limiting-references><application-references><section-title>Application-oriented references</section-title><section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">Examples of places where the subject matter of this place is covered when specially adapted, used for a particular purpose, or incorporated in a larger system:</paragraph-text><table><table-row>
                  <table-column>
