<definition-item><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">E05C5/00</classification-symbol><definition-title>Fastening devices with bolts moving otherwise than only rectilinearly and only pivotally or rotatively {(<class-ref scheme="cpc">E05C9/1883</class-ref>, <class-ref scheme="cpc">E05C19/009</class-ref>, <class-ref scheme="cpc">E05B63/125</class-ref>, <class-ref scheme="cpc">E05B63/126</class-ref>, <class-ref scheme="cpc">E05B63/127</class-ref> take precedence; pivotally-mounted hooks-like fastenings with toggle action <class-ref scheme="cpc">E05C19/14</class-ref>; bayonet-type locks <class-ref scheme="cpc">E05B63/125</class-ref>; locks for sliding wings, with additional movement <class-ref scheme="cpc">E05B65/0817</class-ref>)}</definition-title><definition-statement>
